Select tag

Select select=new Select(element); 
1- SelectByValue
2- selectByVisibleText
3- selectByIndex

NOTE: We can select more than one value from drop down box if we have 'multiple' attribute on select tag. 
DeSelecting the Values from Drop Down box
1- deselectByValue
2- deselectByVisibleText
3- deselectByIndex
4- deselectByAll 

